{"PageNumber":19,"Angle":0,"RotatedAngle":0,"Height":1620,"Width":2880,"OriginHeight":0,"OriginWidth":0,"Elements":[{"Index":0,"Type":"title","Text":"#  Mitigating DDoS","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":219,"Y":305},"LeftTop":{"X":219,"Y":187},"RightBottom":{"X":1075,"Y":305},"RightTop":{"X":1075,"Y":187}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":1,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● In theory, there is no way to completely eliminate the possibility of a DDoS attack, since the bandwidth a server is able to provide its users will always be limited","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":219,"Y":707},"LeftTop":{"X":219,"Y":446},"RightBottom":{"X":2613,"Y":707},"RightTop":{"X":2613,"Y":446}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":2,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● Still, measures may be taken to mitigate the risks of DoS attacks.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":219,"Y":827},"LeftTop":{"X":219,"Y":749},"RightBottom":{"X":2437,"Y":827},"RightTop":{"X":2437,"Y":749}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":3,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● For example, many servers incorporate DoS protection mechanisms that analyse incoming traffic and drop packets from sources that are consuming too much bandwidth","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":219,"Y":1131},"LeftTop":{"X":219,"Y":872},"RightBottom":{"X":2592,"Y":1131},"RightTop":{"X":2592,"Y":872}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":4,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● Unfortunately, IP spoofing may make DDoS prevention more difficult, by obscuring the identity of the attacker bots and providing inconsistent information on where network traffic is coming from","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":219,"Y":1433},"LeftTop":{"X":219,"Y":1172},"RightBottom":{"X":2621,"Y":1433},"RightTop":{"X":2621,"Y":1172}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""}]}